

### Directory Format

```sh
time pg_dump -v \
  -h em-vrai-pgrd48.alpha.ros.gov.uk -p 5432 -U rosdba \
  -d gis \
  -Fd -j 4 \
  --exclude-schema=osmm_archiving \
  --exclude-schema=mapping \
  --no-subscriptions \ 
-f /db/PostgreSQL/dump_restore/gis_alpha.dmp  2>&1 | tee /db/PostgreSQL/dump_restore/gis_dump.log
```

